OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1777284410
OL,3,CArgentina renews call for Falklands
OL,4,Ctalks amid potential shift in US stance
OL,6,FArgentina has called for talks with
OL,7,Fthe UK over the Falkland Islands after
OL,8,Freports the US could review its
OL,9,Fposition on the South Atlantic
OL,10,Fterritory in retaliation for Sir Keir
OL,11,FStarmer's lack of support for the war
OL,12,Fin Iran.
OL,14,FDowning Street had earlier insisted
OL,15,Fthe sovereignty of the Falklands was
OL,16,F"not in question".
OL,26,@xD@AOUxD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
