PN,31902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1777284410
OL,3,CArgentina renews call for Falklands
OL,4,Ctalks amid potential shift in US stance
OL,6,FThat came after an internal Pentagon
OL,7,Femail set out options for President
OL,8,FDonald Trump's administration to
OL,9,Fpunish Nato allies for refusing to
OL,10,Fjoin the US-Israeli strikes against
OL,11,FIran.
OL,13,FThe memo, first reported by Reuters,
OL,14,Fsuggests reassessing US diplomatic
OL,15,Fsupport for "imperial possessions"
OL,16,Fsuch as the Falklands.
OL,18,FArgentina has long claimed sovereignty
OL,19,Fover the Falkland Islands and invaded
OL,20,Fthem in 1982 before being defeated in
OL,21,Fa short but bloody war.
OL,26,@wD@MOUwD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1777284410
OL,3,CArgentina renews call for Falklands
OL,4,Ctalks amid potential shift in US stance
OL,6,FDowning Street said the UK's stance on
OL,7,Fthe Falklands was not going to change.
OL,9,F"The Falkland Islands have previously
OL,10,Fvoted overwhelmingly in favour of
OL,11,Fremaining a UK overseas territory, and
OL,12,Fwe've always stood behind the
OL,13,Fislanders' right to self-determination
OL,14,Fand the fact that sovereignty rests
OL,15,Fwith the UK," a No 10 spokesman said.
OL,26,@qD@AOUwD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
