SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1777284410
OL,3,CArgentina renews call for Falklands
OL,4,Ctalks amid potential shift in US stance
OL,6,F"The question of the Falkland Islands
OL,7,Fand the UK's sovereignty and the
OL,8,Fislanders' right to self-determination
OL,9,Fis not in question, and we've
OL,10,Fexpressed that position clearly and
OL,11,Fconsistently."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@NO]
