OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1777284410
OL,3,CArgentina renews call for Falklands
OL,4,Ctalks amid potential shift in US stance
OL,6,FArgentina's foreign minister Pablo
OL,7,FQuirno posted on X in response: "The
OL,8,FArgentine Republic once again
OL,9,Fexpresses its willingness to resume
OL,10,Fbilateral negotiations with the United
OL,11,FKingdom that will allow for finding a
OL,12,Fpeaceful and definitive solution to
OL,13,Fthe sovereignty dispute and bring an
OL,14,Fend to the special and particular
OL,15,Fcolonial situation in which they are
OL,16,Fimmersed."
OL,26,@oD@aOUxD@JO]
