OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1777284410
OL,3,CArgentina renews call for Falklands
OL,4,Ctalks amid potential shift in US stance
OL,6,FThe Falkland Islands government said
OL,7,Fit had "complete confidence in the
OL,8,Fcommitment made by the UK Government
OL,9,Fto uphold and defend our right of self-
OL,10,Fdetermination".
OL,12,FThe row is the latest sign of the
OL,13,Fstrains in the US-UK relationship as
OL,14,Fthe King and Queen prepare for their
OL,15,Fstate visit on Monday.
OL,17,FDowning Street said it was confident
OL,18,Fthe trip would "showcase the very best
OL,19,Fof the UK-US bilateral relationship".
OL,26,@oD@HOUrD@NO]zD@POU{D@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
