PN,31907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1777284410
OL,3,CArgentina renews call for Falklands
OL,4,Ctalks amid potential shift in US stance
OL,6,FFalklands war veteran Simon Weston
OL,7,Fsaid he hoped the King would be able
OL,8,Fto get the US to "calm down".
OL,10,FAsked what message he hoped Charles
OL,11,Fwould deliver to Mr Trump, he told BBC
OL,12,FNewsnight: "I would hope that he would
OL,13,Fjust kind of get him to back down and
OL,14,Fcalm down over the Falklands.
OL,16,F"What we don't need is Mr Millei to
OL,17,Fraise his sleeves and believe that
OL,18,Faggression may work because that would
OL,19,Fjust cost more lives."
OL,26,@pD@ROUpD@\O]tD@LOUxD@AOU{D@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
