PN,31908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1777284410
OL,3,CArgentina renews call for Falklands
OL,4,Ctalks amid potential shift in US stance
OL,6,FThe US president is an ally of
OL,7,FArgentina's president Javier Milei,
OL,8,Fwhile his relationship with Sir Keir
OL,9,Fhas deteriorated dramatically since
OL,10,Fthe start of the Iran crisis.
OL,12,FThe Prime Minister has refused to give
OL,13,Fthe US free rein in its use of British
OL,14,Fmilitary bases to conduct the bombing
OL,15,Fcampaign against Iran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
