PN,31909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1777284410
OL,3,CArgentina renews call for Falklands
OL,4,Ctalks amid potential shift in US stance
OL,6,FLimited permission was granted for
OL,7,Fbases ` including RAF Fairford in
OL,8,FGloucestershire and Diego Garcia in
OL,9,Fthe British Indian Ocean Territory `
OL,10,Fto be used in defensive actions
OL,11,Fagainst Iran's missile sites and
OL,12,Finstallations threatening the Strait
OL,13,Fof Hormuz, but only after Tehran's
OL,14,Fretaliatory actions began.
OL,16,FThe US State Department describes the
OL,17,FFalklands as "administered by the
OL,18,FUnited Kingdom, claimed by Argentina"
OL,19,Fand uses the Spanish name Islas
OL,20,FMalvinas alongside the English name.
OL,26,@yD@NOUzD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
