PN,31910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1777284410
OL,3,CArgentina renews call for Falklands
OL,4,Ctalks amid potential shift in US stance
OL,6,FThe potential for a shift in the US
OL,7,Fposition has been considered in the
OL,8,FForeign Office although it has been
OL,9,Ftreated as a "hypothetical scenario".
OL,11,FBen Judah, who was a special adviser
OL,12,Fto former foreign secretary David
OL,13,FLammy, said the potential shift had
OL,14,Fbeen considered as a hypothetical
OL,15,Fscenario when he was working in the
OL,16,FForeign Office, and that "the Milei
OL,17,Fissue is actually a concern".
OL,26,@qD@NOUqD@dO]xD@ZOUyD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
