PN,31911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1777284410
OL,3,CArgentina renews call for Falklands
OL,4,Ctalks amid potential shift in US stance
OL,6,FHe suggested converting the islands
OL,7,Ffrom overseas territories to overseas
OL,8,Fkingdoms, represented by MPs elected
OL,9,Fto Westminster.
OL,11,F"If this were already the case, His
OL,12,FMajesty would be visiting Washington
OL,13,Fto see Trump this week as King of the
OL,14,FKingdom of the Falklands," he said.
OL,16,FThe Pentagon email expressed
OL,17,Ffrustration at Nato allies' reluctance
OL,18,Fto grant access, basing and overflight
OL,19,F(ABO) rights for the Iran war.
OL,26,@sD@AOUvD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
