PN,31912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1777284410
OL,3,CArgentina renews call for Falklands
OL,4,Ctalks amid potential shift in US stance
OL,6,FIt suggested Spain could be suspended
OL,7,Ffrom the Nato alliance over its
OL,8,Frefusal to allow bases or airspace to
OL,9,Fbe used to attack Iran.
OL,11,FDowning Street backs Spain's
OL,12,Fmembership of the "absolutely
OL,13,Fcritical" alliance.
OL,15,FReform UK's Nigel Farage said he would
OL,16,Fraise the issue of the Falklands
OL,17,Fpersonally with the Argentinian
OL,18,Fpresident when he visits him later
OL,19,Fthis year and tell him their status is
OL,20,F"non-negotiable".
OL,26,@tD@SOUuD@IO]|D@AOU|D@PO]
