CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1777284410
OL,3,CArgentina renews call for Falklands
OL,4,Ctalks amid potential shift in US stance
OL,6,FTory leader Kemi Badenoch said the US
OL,7,Fstance was "absolute nonsense" and
OL,8,Fcompared it to Mr Trump's comments on
OL,9,FGreenland.
OL,11,FLiberal Democrat leader Sir Ed Davey
OL,12,Fsaid the King's visit to the US should
OL,13,Fbe cancelled, adding: "The state visit
OL,14,Fshould clearly be pulled ` this
OL,15,Funreliable, damaging president cannot
OL,16,Fkeep insulting our country."
OL,26,@oD@LOUoD@^O]uD@WOUxD@\O]
